      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen represents the pinnacle of mechanical preservation, with preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service already performed to exacting standards. The M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) operate with factory-fresh calibration, ensuring optimal torque vectoring and chassis composure. Every aerodynamic component, including the carbon fiber roof, remains in flawless condition. This is a zero-compromise enthusiast vehicle with a linear power delivery to its 8,400 RPM redline and a perfectly maintained subframe and suspension geometry.",
